                        <stringValue>6</stringValue>
                    </value>
                </inputParameters>
                <isRequired>false</isRequired>
            </fields>
            <fields>
                <name>S_Quicker_Quotes_Config_Section1_Column2</name>
                <fieldType>Region</fieldType>
                <fields>
                    <name>DT_Quote_Template_Text</name>
                    <fieldText>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);&quot;&gt;PDFs are generated using Quote Documents. Unfortunately, it&apos;s a bit fiddly to get the Quote Template Id to generate PDFs during the Quick Quote process.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);&quot;&gt;Edit the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/lightning/setup/QuoteTemplateEditor/home&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(1, 118, 211);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;quote document&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);&quot;&gt;, and then find and copy the Quote Id from the Address Bar.  The Id starts with a 0 and is located at:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);&quot;&gt;summlid%3D&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;THIS IS THE ID&amp;gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);&quot;&gt;%26r&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);&quot;&gt;For example, the ID from summlid%3D&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);&quot;&gt;0EH5h000003ibgb&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);&quot;&gt;%26r is &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;0EH5h000003ibgb&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Also provide a label for the Quote Template.  If you wish to use multiple templates, you will need to edit the Flow and add them as additional Choices.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</fieldText>
                    <fieldType>DisplayText</fieldType>
                </fields>
                <fields>
                    <name>IT_Quote_Template_Label</name>
                    <dataType>String</dataType>
                    <fieldText>Quote Template Label</fieldText>
                    <fieldType>InputField</fieldType>
                    <isRequired>true</isRequired>
